{
    "title": "Copo Vazio",
    "artist": "Gilberto Gil",
    "composer": "Gilberto Gil",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(9)\">A7(9)</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É    sempre bom lembrar      Que um copo vazio        Está cheio de ar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(9)\">A7(9)</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É    sempre bom lembrar      Que o ar sombrio de um rosto      Está cheio de um ar vazio</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(9)\">A7(9)</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vazio daquilo que no ar do copo  Ocupa um lugar      É sempre bom lembrar, guardar de cor</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que o ar vazio de um rosto sombri__o Está cheio de dor</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(9)\">A7(9)</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É    sempre bom lembrar      Que um copo vazio        Está cheio de ar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>                                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">      Que o ar no copo Ocupa o lugar do vinho</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>                                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#madd9\">F#madd9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">      Que o vinho busca ocupar o lugar da dor</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>                                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E6/9\">E6/9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">       Que a dor ocupa a metade da verdade     A verdadeira natureza interior</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>                                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7(9)\">E7(9)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>                                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7(9)\">F#7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Uma metade cheia Uma metade vazia         Uma metade tristeza Uma metade alegria</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(9)\">A7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A magia da verdade inteira Todo-poderoso amor</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(9)\">A7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A magia da verdade inteira Todo-podero___so amor</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É sempre bom lembrar      Que um copo vazio     Está cheio de ar</span>\n",
